Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:30.24,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3cFFFFFF\bord3\blur2.5\1aFF}向著遠方  追逐著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.99,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3cFFFFFF\bord3\blur2.5\1aFF}不會退讓
