Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.45,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3cFFFFFF\bord3\blur2.5\1aFF}無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.08,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3cFFFFFF\bord3\blur2.5\1aFF}賭上一切
